---
---

<section id="about" class="home-enhance">
  <div class="home-enhance__container container-main">
    <!-- Left: Text content -->
    <div class="home-enhance__content">
      <h2 class="home-enhance__title">
        Family-Owned.<br/>Concrete-Obsessed.
      </h2>

      <div class="home-enhance__text">
        <p>
          Azteca Concrete Decoration is a family-owned business with one obsession: turning worn, cracked, and ordinary concrete into surfaces that make people stop and stare. We coat, restore, and refinish — with zero shortcuts and zero compromise.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every project gets the same care whether it's a garage floor or a full driveway overhaul. We don't cut corners because our name is on every single job. That's not a tagline — that's how we were raised.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Large photo -->
    <div class="home-enhance__image-wrapper">
      <img
        src="/images/Newly-Coated-Driveway.webp"
        alt="Beautifully coated home entrance and driveway"
        class="home-enhance__image"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .home-enhance {
    background-color: var(--color-fir-500);
    padding-top: var(--space-24);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
    padding-left: var(--container-padding-x);
    padding-right: var(--container-padding-x);
    color: var(--color-white);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .home-enhance {
      padding-left: var(--container-padding-x-lg);
      padding-right: var(--container-padding-x-lg);
    }
  }

  .home-enhance__container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .home-enhance__container {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .home-enhance__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .home-enhance__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    color: var(--color-accent-light);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .home-enhance__title {
      font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    }
  }

  .home-enhance__text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    max-width: 36rem;
    padding-top: var(--space-2);
  }

  .home-enhance__image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    height: min(70vh, 600px);
  }

  .home-enhance__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
</style>
